member.name: T:VulcanVOGUIClasses.Functions
member.summary:
This is the compiler generated class in which all functions are implemented as static methods.
You do not need to use the classname in your code.
The compiler will automatically add a USING STATIC for this class so you can call the methods with a function sytax in your code, just like you would do in Visual Objects
